data.description: ***HUGE PRICE IMPROVEMENT***Nestled in the Sunny View neighborhood, this 1956 vintage home exudes timeless charm and warmth.  Upon entering, you're greeted by the home's warm and welcoming interior. The living room features lovely coved ceilings a large window that floods the space with natural light. The vinyl wood-plank floors have been updated and add a touch of character to the space. The open floor plan allows for versatile furniture arrangement, making it easy to personalize the space according to your taste. The two bedrooms in this home offer comfortable retreats.  Now, let's talk about the unique feature that sets this property apart - the expansive poured concrete driveway. If you're an outdoor enthusiast, this is the perfect space for you. It's generously sized and can easily accommodate your RV and boat.   Never worry about storage or parking again; this property provides a solution for all your recreational vehicle needs. You're within easy reach of local parks, schools, and shopping centers, providing you with convenience and comfort. This property is move-in ready and it's waiting for you.  Welcome home!
